 "is     to                   Good luck!  "}</pre></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><pre>Returns: 
{ "This is a text in several columns.",
 "Your job is to put it all together into a single text that is nicely formatted.",
 "Good luck!" }</pre></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td colspan="2" class="statText">This is the example in the problem statement.
